title: AHS: Apocalypse Episode 7 Breakdown and Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: I could really go for a smoothie right about now.
Vaping Myrtle is my new esthetic.
The "fake movie" bubbles was shooting was homage to a real Tales From The Crypt movie that Joan Collins was also a wife murdering her husband on Christmas.
I'm so glad John Henry is back. When he first appeared on the screen looking like a sexy goth George Micheal, I knew they were going to kill him.
I think the Decapitation Killer dressed up as Santa is a call back to season 2 Asylum. Leigh Emerson was a killer dressed up as Santa and got committed to Briarcliff.
description:
